flowchart TD
    START([POST /v1/chat - user message]) --> AUTH[Validate secret and parse request]
    AUTH --> RESOLVE[Resolve model for project_agent_id from Supabase]
    RESOLVE --> ROUTER_LLM

    subgraph LLM1 [LLM Call #1 - Router]
        ROUTER_LLM[Classify message as rag / db / both]
        ROUTER_LLM --> MODE{Mode result}
    end

    MODE -->|rag| EMBED
    MODE -->|db or both| NOTE_DB[Out of scope in this doc]

    subgraph RAG [RAG Retrieval Path]
        EMBED[Create query embedding] --> MATCH[Supabase RPC match_document_chunks]
        MATCH --> CTX[Build context from retrieved chunks]
    end

    CTX --> FINAL_PROMPT[Build final prompt: system + history + RAG context]

    subgraph LLM2 [LLM Call #2 - Final Answer]
        FINAL_PROMPT --> ANSWER_LLM[Generate assistant reply]
    end

    ANSWER_LLM --> FOLLOWUP_PROMPT[Build follow-up suggestion prompt]

    subgraph LLM3 [LLM Call #3 - Suggestions]
        FOLLOWUP_PROMPT --> SUGGEST_LLM[Generate exactly 3 suggestions]
    end

    SUGGEST_LLM --> RESPONSE[Assemble response JSON]
    RESPONSE --> RETURN([Return reply + suggestions + sources])

    %% Latency guide (observed ranges)
    START -.-> L_START[0.05s-0.2s API entry and validation]
    RESOLVE -.-> L_RESOLVE[0.5s-1.2s model/config reads]
    ROUTER_LLM -.-> L_ROUTER[2s-5s]
    EMBED -.-> L_EMBED[0.3s-1s]
    MATCH -.-> L_MATCH[0.3s-0.8s]
    ANSWER_LLM -.-> L_ANSWER[3s-6s]
    SUGGEST_LLM -.-> L_SUGGEST[3s-5s]
    RETURN -.-> L_TOTAL[Typical RAG total: 11s-17s]

    classDef llm fill:#ffe9b3,stroke:#b58100,color:#111;
    classDef infra fill:#e6f4ff,stroke:#1f6fb2,color:#111;
    classDef note fill:#f4f4f4,stroke:#777,color:#111;

    class ROUTER_LLM,ANSWER_LLM,SUGGEST_LLM llm;
    class AUTH,RESOLVE,EMBED,MATCH,CTX,FINAL_PROMPT,FOLLOWUP_PROMPT,RESPONSE infra;
    class NOTE_DB note;
